Augustus Carney https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Augustus_Carney 0 Augustus Carney (1870 – 1920) was an American actor during the early 1900s. Born in Ireland in 1870, he got his start in vaudeville before entering the film industry. In his short seven-year career he appeared in over 130 films, mostly shorts.
